G̹nther, 1887:124 (subgenus of 
<taxonomicName authority="Bloch, 1786" authorityName="Bloch" authorityYear="1786" box="[621,716,279,300]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Pleuronectidae" genus="Macrurus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Pleuronectiformes" pageId="280" pageNumber="281" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">
